{
  "page": "Lonely Light",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Location_map_Iron_Islands.svg\" class=\"image\" title=\"The Iron Islands and the location of the Lonely Light\"><img alt=\"The Iron Islands and the location of the Lonely Light\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/48/Location_map_Iron_Islands.svg/400px-Location_map_Iron_Islands.svg.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"160\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/48/Location_map_Iron_Islands.svg/600px-Location_map_Iron_Islands.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/48/Location_map_Iron_Islands.svg/800px-Location_map_Iron_Islands.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 45.7%; left: 16.7%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -3px; top: -3px; width: 5px; font-size: 5px;\"><img alt=\"The Iron Islands and the location of the Lonely Light\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/5px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Lonely Light\" width=\"5\" height=\"5\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/10px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Lonely Light</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a> and the location of the Lonely Light\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Lonely Light</b> is the westernmost island of the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a>. A beacon blazes at all times on the roof of the island's namesake keep,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> which is the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Farwynd_of_the_Lonely_Light\" title=\"House Farwynd of the Lonely Light\">House Farwynd of the Lonely Light</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Geography\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Geography</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Geography\">Geography</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lonely_Light&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Geography\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Martina_Pilcerovathelonelylights.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e6/Martina_Pilcerovathelonelylights.jpg/350px-Martina_Pilcerovathelonelylights.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"252\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e6/Martina_Pilcerovathelonelylights.jpg/525px-Martina_Pilcerovathelonelylights.jpg 1.5x, /images/e/e6/Martina_Pilcerovathelonelylights.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Martina_Pilcerovathelonelylights.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The Lonely Light, by Martina Pilcerova © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>While most of the Iron Islands lie in <a href=\"/index.php/Ironman%27s_Bay\" title=\"Ironman&#39;s Bay\">Ironman's Bay</a>, there is a smaller group of thirteen islands<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> clustered around the Lonely Light lying eight days sail northwest of <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Wyk\" title=\"Great Wyk\">Great Wyk</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> It lies well into the <a href=\"/index.php/Sunset_Sea\" title=\"Sunset Sea\">Sunset Sea</a> and is probably the most westerly location in the <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> aside from the isles <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon,_Rhaenys,_and_Visenya_(islands)\" title=\"Aegon, Rhaenys, and Visenya (islands)\">Aegon, Rhaenys, and Visenya</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The Lonely Light is surrounded by <a href=\"/index.php/Rookeries\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Rookeries\">rookeries</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Seal\" title=\"Seal\">seals</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Sea_lion\" title=\"Sea lion\">sea lions</a> and ocean.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaflonely_light.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaflonely_light.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> Some say that <a href=\"/index.php/House_Farwynd_of_the_Lonely_Light\" title=\"House Farwynd of the Lonely Light\">House Farwynd of the Lonely Light</a> and their <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a> sleep with seals to birth half-human children, and others claim they are <a href=\"/index.php/Skinchangers\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skinchangers\">skinchangers</a> who take the forms of sea lions, <a href=\"/index.php/Walrus\" title=\"Walrus\">walruses</a>, and spotted <a href=\"/index.php/Whale\" title=\"Whale\">whales</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lonely_Light&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>A thousand years after the time of King <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark_(Burner)\" title=\"Brandon Stark (Burner)\">Brandon the Burner</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> sailing out of <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Wyk\" title=\"Great Wyk\">Great Wyk</a> were blown off course to a cluster of islands eight days sail from the closest shore. Their captain built a tower and a beacon there, took the name \"<a href=\"/index.php/House_Farwynd_of_the_Lonely_Light\" title=\"House Farwynd of the Lonely Light\">Farwynd</a>\", and declared the Lonely Light his seat.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lonely_Light&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lonely_Light&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gylbert_Farwynd\" title=\"Gylbert Farwynd\">Gylbert Farwynd</a> and his sons <a href=\"/index.php/Gyles_Farwynd\" title=\"Gyles Farwynd\">Gyles</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Ygon_Farwynd\" title=\"Ygon Farwynd\">Ygon</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Yohn_Farwynd\" title=\"Yohn Farwynd\">Yohn</a> depart the Lonely Light to attend the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsmoot_on_Old_Wyk\" title=\"Kingsmoot on Old Wyk\">kingsmoot on Old Wyk</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lonely_Light&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Aeron knew some <a href=\"/index.php/House_Farwynd\" title=\"House Farwynd\">Farwynds</a>, a queer folk who held lands on the westernmost shores of <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Wyk\" title=\"Great Wyk\">Great Wyk</a> and the scattered isles beyond, rocks so small that most could support but a single household. Of those, the Lonely Light was the most distant, eight days' sail to the northwest amongst rookeries of <a href=\"/index.php/Seal\" title=\"Seal\">seals</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Sea_lion\" title=\"Sea lion\">sea lions</a> and the boundless grey oceans. The <a href=\"/index.php/House_Farwynd_of_the_Lonely_Light\" title=\"House Farwynd of the Lonely Light\">Farwynds there</a> were even queerer than the rest. Some said they were <a href=\"/index.php/Skinchanger\" title=\"Skinchanger\">skinchangers</a>, unholy creatures who could take on the forms of <a href=\"/index.php/Sea_lion\" title=\"Sea lion\">sea lions</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Walrus\" title=\"Walrus\">walruses</a>, even <a href=\"/index.php/Whale\" title=\"Whale\">spotted whales</a>, the wolves of <a href=\"/index.php/Sunset_Sea\" title=\"Sunset Sea\">the wild sea</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Aeron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Aeron Greyjoy\">Aeron Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lonely_Light&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Iron Islands.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raff